sets.summary: Go full-body and full throttle to ensure you don't miss a muscle.
sets.subTitle: Centr Power in Gym: Intermediate week 4

workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
There are only 2 rounds in this workout, but you'll be doing big reps in even bigger supersets to get your full body pumping.


Get your form for these new moves down using the tutorial.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Get your muscles firing and ready to lift.

Dumbbell single-arm seated press right (25% lifting weight)
Dumbbell single-arm seated press left (50% lifting weight)
Dumbbell single-arm seated press right (50% lifting weight)
Dumbbell single-arm seated press left (75% lifting weight)
Dumbbell single-arm seated press right (75% lifting weight)

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: Tempo is essential with high reps and three lifts back to back, so count it out.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: Hit your lower body to build the burn in your glutes and calves.
